Garden tab

Tap Draw Shape then click on the canvas to outline your garden
Once you have 3+ points, switch to Place Plants
Click inside your garden shape to add a plant
Choose your plant and soil type
Tap a plant to see its health, watering schedule and history
Press "I watered this plant" when you water it

Encyclopedia tab

Browse all 20 plants
Search by name, family or origin
Tap any plant for full care stats

Profile tab

Tap your avatar to set a profile photo
Tap your name to edit it
Share your friend code with teammates to connect
Change the app theme at the bottom

Tips
use this link: https://plot34.netlify.app
Use Chrome for the best experience
Your data saves automatically in your browser
The ? button on each screen explains how it works


